      About this item

      • Controls Caseta smart switches and dimmers from Lutron
      • Add an additional point of control wirelessly, without needing a hub or password, for maximum convenience
      • Seamlessly match the look and feel of the Diva smart dimmer and Claro smart switch with a consistent aesthetic
      • Exclusively with the Diva smart dimmer: Tap once for preset slider level, double tap for full brightness (may require firmware update for feature; hub required for update)
      • Place on the wall with a wallmount bracket (PICO-WBX-ADAPT, sold separately), place on a pedestal (L-PED1-WH, sold separately) or use from your hand
      • Mount on almost any wall surface with a wallmount bracket to add a 2nd "switch" anywhere you need it - no cutting holes or pulling wire required (easy wireless 3-way)
      • Worry-free: pico remotes typically have a 10-year battery life
      • Pico remotes can be paired with multiple Caseta dimmers or switches enabling them to control the lighting of an entire room
      • Works with the entire Caseta family of products, including the original Caseta aesthetic dimmers and switches, the Diva and Claro smart aesthetics, lamp dimmers and the outdoor smart plug
      • Includes (1) Pico paddle remote for Caseta smart switches and dimmers; additional accessories sold separately

      Product Description

      The Lutron family of Pico smart remotes gives you easy, flexible control of your Caseta smart light switches, Serena smart shades, fans, SONOS speakers and more. With the Pico paddle remote for Caseta smart switches and dimmers, you can match the paddle-style of the Diva smart dimmer and Claro smart switch, creating a consistent aesthetic. The Pico smart remote looks and feels just like a regular switch - add it to any room without cutting holes or pulling wire in the wall to install. Create a wireless 3-way application by mounting on the wall with a Pico wallmount bracket (PICO-WBX-ADAPT, sold separately). Pair with multiple Caseta dimmers or switches at one time, enabling one Pico remote to control the lighting of an entire room. Exclusively with the Diva smart dimmer, one tap of the Pico paddle remote brings lights to the level set on the dimmer and 2 taps goes to full brightness. The Pico paddle remote works with the entire Caseta family of products, including the original Caseta aesthetic dimmers and switches, the Diva and Claro smart aesthetic of dimmers and switches, lamp dimmers and the outdoor smart plug. With a typical 10-year battery life, you can be confident your Pico will continue to work when you need it. Includes (1) Pico paddle remote for Caseta dimmers and switches; accessories like the wallmount bracket (PICO-WBX-ADAPT) are sold separately.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

I have smart bulbs and I thought I'd be able to use this to control them with home assistant, but no. It doesn't pair with the hub, it only pairs with other switches.

It's also hard to tell if you've pressed it by feel alone, because it's very quiet. So quiet that if you have it installed over a switch box, you can hear the hollow space behind the remote.
